import Stack from '@mui/material/Stack';
function main(){
    return(<>
    <form>
        <Stack direction="row" spacing={2}>
            <label>
            Year:
            <input type="text" name="year" />
            </label>
            <label>
            Month:
            <input type="text" name="month" />
            </label>
            <label>
            Day:
            <input type="text" name="day" />
            </label>
            <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
        </Stack>
        
    </form>
    </>)
}

export default main;
